memberdef.name: _operators
memberdef.initializer: = { '<': lambda v, c, p: v < c, '>': lambda v, c, p: v > c, '<=': lambda v, c, p: v == c or v < c, '>=': lambda v, c, p: v == c or v > c, '==': lambda v, c, p: v == c, '===': lambda v, c, p: v == c, # by default, compatible => >=. '~=': lambda v, c, p: v == c or v > c, '!=': lambda v, c, p: v != c, }

para.verbatim:
Check if the provided version matches the constraints.
:param version: The version to match against this instance. :type version: String or :class:`Version` instance.
